{"word":"H3573 - כּוּשַׁן רִשְׁעָתַיִם - Kûwshan Rishʻâthayim - koo-shan' rish-awthah'-yim - Chushan-rishathayim","slug":"H3573","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כּוּשַׁן רִשְׁעָתַיִם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Kûwshan Rishʻâthayim"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>koo-shan' rish-awthah'-yim"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chushan-rishathayim"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DF; &#x05E8;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E2;&#x05EA;&#x05D9;&#x05DD; - ku&#x0302;shan rish&#x201B;a&#x0302;thayim</b> - <i>koo-shan' rish-aw-thah'-yim</i><p/>Apparently from <a href=\"#/H3572\">H3572</a> and the dual of <a href=\"#/H7564\">H7564</a>; <i>Cushan of double wickedness</i>; <i>Cushan-Rishathajim</i>, a Mesopotamian king: - Chushan-rishathayim."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3568\">H3568</a>, <a href=\"#/H3569\">H3569</a>, <a href=\"#/H3570\">H3570</a>, <a href=\"#/H3571\">H3571</a>, <a href=\"#/H3572\">H3572</a>, <a href=\"#/H3575\">H3575</a>"}]}